\begin_layout Plain Layout
and others? Abdel
\end_layout

\end_inset

 For 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, it ensures that the total amount of status is constant over generations.
 Note that in proposition XXX, we took 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{c(i)}=\bar{g}_{i}$
\end_inset

 and likewise for 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{c(i)}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

